To identify unique sku to be added as the commerce item we need below details:

{color:#000000}autoZoneSKU = ?0 AND partNumber = ?1 AND lineCode = ?2 AND brandId = ?3 AND type = ?4{color}

The details what we get in the cxml from carvana based on [^CarvanaPO.txt]
 * {color:#000000}{color:#000000}partNumber & lineCode ( from {color}{color}<SupplierPartID>CHL:S11473</SupplierPartID> in line item)
 * {color:#000000}{color:#000000} autoZoneSKU (assuming {color}{color}<Extrinsic name="part_line_id">3556360</Extrinsic> is azSkuId in line item)

{color:#000000}we will also need brand/brandId and type of sku ie. partSku or accessory{color}

